data.description: 1805 Florida Avenue, a stunning 1925 Mediterranean Revival welcomes you at the entrance of the highly sought after neighborhood, Historic Flamingo Park. Completely rebuilt in 2015, this home offers classic charm with an open floor plan with modern amenities. Boasting sunlit rooms throughout, there are 5 large bedrooms, 3 baths and 1 bed/bath casita. The chef's kitchen opens to a spacious living room. Glass French doors lead to a peaceful backyard with a heated pool, patio, lush landscaping. Walk/bike to Antique Row, The Norton Museum, premier shops, restaurants like Hive, Joseph's, Bedner's, Konro, Table 26, Grato and Rosemary Square. Palm Beach Island, PBI airport minutes away. Zoned for Palm Beach Public School. Don't miss this captivating home.
